cture Health`,desc:`Code quality analysis dashboard ŌĆö detects God Modules, orphan files, pain zone modules, and high cyclomatic complexity. Generates a health score with actionable suggestions.`,tech:`Cyclomatic complexity analysis ┬Ę Martin instability/abstractness metrics ┬Ę coupling analysis ┬Ę clone detection ┬Ę health scoring algorithm`},history:{title:`Version History`,desc:`Browse complete commit timeline with file-level diffs. Rollback to any previous version or restore individual files. All rollbacks are undoable.`,tech:`SHA-256 content-addressed storage ┬Ę diff-match-patch ┬Ę isomorphic-git bridge ┬Ę snapshot-based versioning`},settings:{title:`Project Settings`,desc:`Configure Git remote sync, auto-snapshot scheduling, external REST API server, data verification, and version rollback.`,tech:`Express 5 REST API ┬Ę Socket.IO ┬Ę isomorphic-git ┬Ę Electron IPC ┬Ę Bearer token auth ┬Ę Windows context menu integration`},about:{title:`About DBHT`,desc:`Learn about DBHT ŌĆö DeepBlueHarnessTrace. Revisit the onboarding guide, connect with the author, and support the project.`,tech:`Electron 28 ┬Ę React 19 ┬Ę TypeScript ┬Ę Vite 8 ┬Ę local-first architecture ┬Ę free and open-source`}},vector:{title:`Vector Knowledge Base`,indexStatus:`Index Status`,buildIndex:`Build Knowledge Base`,rebuildIndex:`Rebuild Knowledge Base`,deleteIndex:`Delete Knowledge Base`,buildBtn:`ŌÜĪ Vectorize & Build`,stepSource:`­¤ōź Source Files`,knowledgeBase:`­¤ōŖ Knowledge Base`,buildDesc:`Parse source files into semantic vectors for AI-powered code search`,noIndexHint:`Click the button above to build a knowledge base from your source code and documents`,semanticSearch:`Semantic Search`,searchPlaceholder:`Enter search query (natural language)...`,search:`Search`,topK:`Top K`,minSimilarity:`Min Similarity`,results:`Results`,noIndex:`No index built yet. Click "Build Index" to create a semantic search index for this project.`,model:`Model`,dimensions:`Dimensions`,chunks:`Chunks`,files:`Files`,