 Unstable modules should be abstract, stable modules should be concrete. Review the D-metric for each module.`,sug_circular_deps_title:`{count} Circular Dependencies`,sug_circular_deps_desc:`Cycles create tight coupling and make testing/refactoring difficult. Break cycles by extracting interfaces or using dependency inversion.`,sug_high_complexity_title:`High Average Complexity`,sug_high_complexity_desc:`Average cyclomatic complexity is {value}. Extract complex logic into smaller functions and reduce nesting depth.`,sug_clone_groups_title:`{count} Clone Group(s) Detected`,sug_clone_groups_desc:`Files with the same name in different directories may indicate code duplication. Consider extracting shared logic into a shared module.`,sug_healthy_title:`Architecture looks healthy`,sug_healthy_desc:`No significant issues detected. Continue following good practices: keep modules small, manage dependencies, and refactor regularly.`},overview:{repo:`Repo`,changes:`Changes`,files:`Files`,added:`Added`,modified:`Modified`,deleted:`Deleted`,getStatus:`Get Status`,update:`Update`,info:`Info`,openFolder:`Open Folder`,commitChanges:`Commit Changes`,diffStats:`Diff Stats:`,lines:`lines`,file:`file`,files_lc:`files`,noChanges:`Working copy matches latest version ŌĆö no changes.`,gettingStatus:`Getting status...`,updating:`Updating to latest version...`,updated:`Updated to latest version.`,gettingInfo:`Getting repository info...`,gotInfo:`Repository info loaded.`,noChangedFiles:`No changed files detected`,openCommitFailed:`Failed to open commit panel`,clickGetStatus:`Click "Get Status" to view changed files`,noRemote:`Not connected to remote repository`,connectRemote:`Connect Remote`,repoInfo:`Repository Info`,close:`Close`,dbhtSync:`DBHT sync`},settings:{gitRemote:`Git Remote Repository`,remoteRepo:`Remote Repository`,branch:`Branch`,authorName:`Author Name`,authorEmail:`Author Email`,disconnect:`Disconnect Remote`,noRemote:`Not connected to a remote Git repository. Connect to enable